task.summary: Grouped files into packages, added a function to determine position of the nodes for the Map visualization, added a basic Bayes Filter class.
added HistogramFilter which uses odometry and the colour sensor
fixed some lines to account for 1D
added Markov Chain Localization and fixed some lines in ParticleFilter and GridLocalization
added byte shift to get large values from arduino
added another shift to get 2nd encoder reading
